      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional vehicle maintained to the highest possible standards. This specimen exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. With no discernible wear and an interior that remains in a pristine, original state, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands excellence without compromise. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the most rigorous standards of automotive preservation.",
