      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is flawless, featuring original factory paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, with supple leather, zero bolster wear, and original floor mats. This car has a smoke-free and pet-free history, and it has never been driven in inclement weather. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of every service record since its delivery. Every button, sensor, and feature operates with factory precision. This is an investment-grade example for the most discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
